      "updated_at": "2016-04-02 23:56:50 UTC",
      "body": "Is there a scalariform (or similar) plugin that can be reused except with scalafmt? Is it possible to automatically upgrade the plugin as part of a [publish script](https://github.com/olafurpg/scalafmt/blob/master/bin/publish.sh)?\r\n\r\nI don't use gradle personally so I would think it is better for someone who uses it to be involved."
    },
