      "updated_at": "2016-04-03 00:09:39 UTC",
      "body": "I think the plugins are distributed through Maven Central.\r\n\r\nI don't know scalariform (and couldn't find it for gradle in a quick search), but from my links above, it seems to be pretty easy to add a new gradle task that just calls into a jar. That way we could run `gradle scalafmt assemble` to format and build."
    },
