      "updated_at": "2016-04-03 11:20:43 UTC",
      "body": "Sounds great, I'm sure it's not a lot of work for someone with gradle experience. It would require more effort for me since I have never used gradle!\r\n\r\nI'm happy to assist anyone who wants to contribute such a plugin. We can make it part of the scalafmt build so the plugin is released alongside scalafmt."
